 *   Web Token (JWT) generation.
 * 
 *   **IMPORTANT FOR USERS**: You must replace the placeholder values (like
 *   "YOUR_DATABASE_HOST", "YOUR_PASSWORD_HERE", etc.) with your actual
 *   development environment settings. Do not use these settings in production.
 *   Remove the comments before deploying to production. 
